    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It's in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the heavy dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
