    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled. The chassis is structurally immaculate, having undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolsters are flawless, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous mechanical stewardship. Recent Blackstone oil analysis confirms the integrity of the rod bearings, ensuring this S54 is track-ready or collection-worthy.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
